{"type": "article", "id": 27544, "title": "动物时钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-31T07:01:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702123008AtcUesCvE02NHaJo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>英国设计师 Paul Farrell 最近推出了一个动物园时钟系列，包含了五种不同动物的木质时钟。Farrell 以抽象的动物脸部图案作为钟面，并且通过动物的花纹表示刻度，非常可爱。这是挂钟的<a href=\"http://www.byshop.co/shop/\">购买链接</a>，售价为 48.30 英镑（<a href=\"http://www.byshop.co/shop/bjorn-polar-bear-clock\">白熊款</a>为 48.39 英镑）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123006CQfKiAPushWYHeMX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123006XaWYmnhDsVrKv8UH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123007VTisW1XUQx4wNrYh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123007McrEiu0ZBy4HzRWd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}